#

Spicy Jalapeño Guacamole

10 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerDipSpicyHealthy

Description

A creamy and zesty avocado dip with a spicy kick, perfect for snacking or as a topping.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • jalapeño, finely chopped: 1
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • cilantro, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: to taste
